<head>
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Work Assignment & Scheduling</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    /* ========= <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Work Assignment & Scheduling Page ========= */

    .as-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-green: #16a34a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 72px;
    }

    .as-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .as-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */

    .as-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .as-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .as-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .as-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .as-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.2vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .as-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .as-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .as-hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .as-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .as-hero-foot {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .as-hero-foot span {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .as-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .as-hero-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      padding: 18px 18px 18px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .as-hero-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .as-hero-chip {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    }

    .as-hero-status {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .as-hero-topline {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .as-hero-topline span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .as-hero-topline strong {
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .as-hero-map {
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 10px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.35);
    }

    .as-hero-map-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .as-hero-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .as-hero-pill {
      padding: 3px 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.55);
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
    }

    .as-hero-map-body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .as-hero-map-main {
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), rgba(15, 23, 42, 1));
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 120px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
    }

    .as-hero-map-main::before {
      content: "Optimised routes · Live view";
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      left: 10px;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .as-hero-map-dot {
      position: absolute;
      width: 7px;
      height: 7px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .as-hero-map-dot.red {
      background: #f97316;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.9);
    }

    .as-hero-map-dot.blue {
      background: #60a5fa;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.9);
    }

    .as-hero-map-list {
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .as-hero-map-item-head,
    .as-hero-map-item-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 0.9fr 0.7fr;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .as-hero-map-item-head {
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .as-hero-map-item-row strong {
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .as-hero-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    .as-hero-meta code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
        "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .as-hero-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .as-hero-footer span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .as-hero-footer-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .as-hero-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ---------- Intro ---------- */

    .as-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .as-intro h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .as-intro p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .as-intro strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- Section headings ---------- */

    .as-section-heading {
      margin: 40px 0 16px;
    }

    .as-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .as-section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .as-section-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    /* ---------- Feature cards ---------- */

    .as-feature-group {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .as-feature-group {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .as-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .as-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .as-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .as-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .as-feature-list {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .as-feature-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .as-feature-note {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    /* ---------- Testimonials ---------- */

    .as-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 52px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .as-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .as-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .as-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    }

    .as-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .as-testimonial-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .as-testimonial-heading {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .as-testimonial-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .as-testimonial-person {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .as-testimonial-person strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- Articles ---------- */

    .as-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .as-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .as-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .as-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .as-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .as-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .as-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .as-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .as-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .as-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- Newsletter ---------- */

    .as-newsletter {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #111827, #020617);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .as-newsletter {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .as-newsletter h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .as-newsletter p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .as-newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .as-newsletter-input {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      min-width: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      outline: none;
    }

    .as-newsletter-input::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .as-newsletter-btn {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .as-newsletter-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="as-page" id="assignment-scheduling">
  <div class="as-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="as-hero">
      <div>
        <h1 class="as-title">
          Assign jobs, manage shifts <span>and plan your week with confidence.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="as-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> gives you everything you need to assign jobs, plan routes and organise shifts for
          mobile teams. See the whole week, optimise travel and keep everyone working on the right
          jobs at the right time.
        </p>
        <p class="as-hero-note">
          Perfect for appointment-based work across multiple locations where every minute and every
          mile matters.
        </p>

        <div class="as-cta-row">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">Which plan?</a>
        </div>
        <p class="as-hero-foot">
          <span>Assignments, routes, customers, invoicing and payments — all in <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: assignment & scheduling mockup -->
      <div class="as-hero-media">
        <div class="as-hero-card">
          <div class="as-hero-header">
            <div class="as-hero-chip"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> · Work Assignment</div>
            <div class="as-hero-status">Routes optimised</div>
          </div>

          <div class="as-hero-topline">
            <span>Jobs today: <strong>68 scheduled</strong></span>
            <span>Workers active: <strong>7</strong></span>
          </div>

          <div class="as-hero-map">
            <div class="as-hero-map-header">
              <span>Day Pilot · Map view</span>
              <div class="as-hero-pill-row">
                <span class="as-hero-pill">Route A · Liam</span>
                <span class="as-hero-pill">Route B · Emma</span>
                <span class="as-hero-pill">Route C · Tom</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="as-hero-map-body">
              <div class="as-hero-map-main">
                <!-- Fake map dots -->
                <div class="as-hero-map-dot" style="top: 40%; left: 22%;"></div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-dot blue" style="top: 28%; left: 60%;"></div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-dot red" style="top: 64%; left: 52%;"></div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-dot" style="top: 55%; left: 18%;"></div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-dot blue" style="top: 32%; left: 36%;"></div>
              </div>

              <div class="as-hero-map-list">
                <div class="as-hero-map-item-head">
                  <span>Job</span>
                  <span>Worker</span>
                  <span>Status</span>
                </div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-item-row">
                  <span><strong>High Street · Shopfronts</strong></span>
                  <span>Liam</span>
                  <span>In route</span>
                </div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-item-row">
                  <span>Oakview Estate · Route B</span>
                  <span>Emma</span>
                  <span>Scheduled</span>
                </div>
                <div class="as-hero-map-item-row">
                  <span>Riverside Offices</span>
                  <span>Tom</span>
                  <span>Completed</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="as-hero-meta">
            View: <code>Assignments · Today · Optimised by travel time</code>
          </div>

          <div class="as-hero-footer">
            <span>
              <span class="as-hero-footer-dot"></span>
              Auto-calc best route for each worker
            </span>
            <span>Reassign jobs with drag &amp; drop</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="as-hero-shadow"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="as-intro">
      <h2>Organise and plan jobs for the most efficient workflow.</h2>
      <p>
        If your work is appointment-based and spread across different areas, route optimisation isn’t a
        luxury — it’s what keeps your day profitable. Manually reshuffling jobs and updating worksheets
        slows everything down.
      </p>
      <p>
        <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>’s assignment and scheduling tools help you plan faster, reduce wasted travel and keep
        your team moving smoothly from job to job.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Stop fighting the schedule and start using it as a competitive advantage.</strong>
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- SECTION: ORGANISE & PLAN -->
    <section>
      <div class="as-section-heading">
        <p class="as-section-kicker">Planning</p>
        <h2 class="as-section-title">Plan your week once and let <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> do the heavy lifting.</h2>
        <p class="as-section-sub">
          Build schedules that respect travel time, worker availability and customer expectations — with
          tools that update in real time as things change.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="as-feature-group">
        <!-- Organise jobs & shifts -->
        <article class="as-feature-card">
          <p class="as-feature-label">Organise Jobs &amp; Shifts</p>
          <h3 class="as-feature-title">Build clear schedules for every worker and team</h3>
          <p class="as-feature-text">
            Start with your confirmed jobs and planned shifts. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> lets you drop them into a
            structured view by day, worker, route or team. Everyone sees what’s ahead and where they
            need to be.
          </p>
          <ul class="as-feature-list">
            <li>View jobs by worker, team, round or area</li>
            <li>Quickly spot gaps, overlaps and heavy days</li>
            <li>Filter by job type, status or priority</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="as-feature-note">
            Ideal for owners and dispatchers who want a calm, predictable day — even when it’s busy.
          </p>
        </article>

        <!-- Weekly planning -->
        <article class="as-feature-card">
          <p class="as-feature-label">Weekly Planning</p>
          <h3 class="as-feature-title">Plan days—or full weeks—at once</h3>
          <p class="as-feature-text">
            Create daily or weekly assignment plans that fit how your business runs. Schedule recurring
            work, one-off visits and responsive jobs together without losing sight of capacity.
          </p>
          <ul class="as-feature-list">
            <li>Switch between daily and weekly planning views</li>
            <li>Set targets for each route or worker</li>
            <li>Block out time for travel, training or maintenance</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="as-feature-note">
            When the plan is set, <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> keeps everyone in sync across web and mobile.
          </p>
        </article>
